<paragraph id="8BF136C4FFD2810F69E0FB44FE17FB53" blockId="60.[189,399,1187,1213]" box="[189,399,1187,1213]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">
<heading id="D0B981A8FFD2810F69E0FB44FE17FB53" bold="true" box="[189,399,1187,1213]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" reason="3">
<emphasis id="B93AEAD6FFD2810F69E0FB44FE17FB53" bold="true" box="[189,399,1187,1213]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">Taxonomic notes</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF136C4FFD2810F69E0FB35FE10FA97" blockId="60.[189,1400,1233,1401]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">
<bibRefCitation id="EFDF4B35FFD2810F69E0FB35FE0DFB02" author="Martynova O. M." box="[189,405,1233,1260]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" pagination="69 - 94" refId="ref40094" refString="Martynova O. M. 1958. Novye nasekomye iz Permskikh i Mezozoiskikh otlozhenii SSSR. Materialy k Osnovam Paleontologii 2: 69 - 94." type="journal article" year="1958">Martynova (1958)</bibRefCitation>
described the genus † 
<emphasis id="B93AEAD6FFD2810F6BC3FB36FCE9FB05" box="[670,881,1233,1259]" italics="true" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">Tychtodelopterum</emphasis>
based on a single species from the Russian Permian, placing it in the family † 
<taxonomicName id="4C4E4D47FFD2810F6B34FB12FB9AFAE1" authority="Guthorl, 1939" authorityName="Guthorl" authorityYear="1939" box="[617,1026,1269,1295]" class="Insecta" family="Archaemiopteridae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Archaemiopteridae Guthorl, 1939</taxonomicName>
(† 
<taxonomicName id="4C4E4D47FFD2810F6D7FFB12FB25FAFE" authorityName="Martynov" authorityYear="1928" box="[1058,1213,1269,1296]" class="Insecta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Miomoptera" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="order">Miomoptera</taxonomicName>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="EFDF4B35FFD2810F6D88FB12FE94FADC" author="Ponomarenko A. G." pageId="60" pageNumber="61" pagination="78 - 86" refId="ref43177" refString="Ponomarenko A. G. 1977. Paleozoiskie predstaviteli vislokrylok (Insecta, Megaloptera). Paleontological Journal 1977 (1): 78 - 86." type="journal article" year="1977">Ponomarenko (1977)</bibRefCitation>
created for this genus the new family † 
<taxonomicName id="4C4E4D47FFD2810F6B83FAFFFC5EFADC" authorityName="Ponomarenko" authorityYear="1977" box="[734,966,1304,1330]" class="Insecta" family="Tychtodelopteridae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Megaloptera" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Tychtodelopteridae</taxonomicName>
, placing it in 
<taxonomicName id="4C4E4D47FFD2810F6D35FAFFFA98FADC" authorityName="Martins &amp; Ardila-Camacho &amp; Rivera-Gasperín &amp; Oswald &amp; Liu &amp; Contreras-Ramos" authorityYear="2022" box="[1128,1280,1304,1330]" class="Insecta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Megaloptera" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="order">Megaloptera</taxonomicName>
. Here, we follow 
<bibRefCitation id="EFDF4B35FFD2810F684FFADCFD94FABB" author="Novokshonov V. G." box="[274,524,1339,1365]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" pagination="194 - 199" refId="ref42114" refString="Novokshonov V. G. 2002. Order Panorpida Latreille, 1802. In: Rasnitsyn A. P. &amp; Quicke D. L. J. (eds) History of Insects: 194 - 199. Kluwer Academic Press, Dordrecht." type="book chapter" year="2002">Novokshonov (2002)</bibRefCitation>
in treating † 
<taxonomicName id="4C4E4D47FFD2810F6BC3FADCFC1BFABB" authorityName="Ponomarenko" authorityYear="1977" box="[670,899,1339,1365]" class="Insecta" family="Tychtodelopteridae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Megaloptera" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Tychtodelopteridae</taxonomicName>
as a synonym of † 
